General.Name: HyTerra Ltd.
General.Description: Hyterra Ltd focuses on the exploration and production of natural hydrogen. It has an interest in a joint venture that includes the wildcat well targeting natural hydrogen in Nebraska, the United States. The company was formerly known as Triple Energy Ltd. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Subiaco, Australia.
